'''Action Deafness''', formerly the Leicester & County Mission for the Deaf, is a British Deaf-led [[Charitable organization|registered charity]] (charitable company limited by guarantee) providing services for the [[Hearing impairment|profoundly deaf]], hard of hearing and the deafened.  The organisation, founded in June 1897 in [[Leicester]], [[England]], headed by Chief Executive Craig Crowley MBE and is accredited in both ISO9001 Quality Management and ISO27001 Information & Security.

